Found a bug, need a feature?
Head to git issues for solution - Issues | github.com
Contributors and feature requests welcome. Bounties may speed up the development process and help to decide which feature will be included next.	Tags: CDN, flickr, gallery, images, photo, responsive	Requires: 3.7.0 or higher
Compatible up to: 3.9.1
